title: The Diary of Bink Cummings Vol 3.5
description: Fat and pregnant, I'm at the end of my rope with swollen ankles and exhaustion. Growing a little person inside of me is no small feat, and when that same little person decides it's time to be welcomed into the world, I'm suddenly catapulted into the beauty of motherhood. Join me in my birthing journey. You're in for one helluva ride.    Must Read Vol's 1-3 First. --Novella.
author: Bink Cummings
